# Static site (canonical)

- **Work in `site/` only** — HTML pages, `css/main.css`, `js/*.js`, images, fonts.
- No Astro, no build step, no `src/` for new changes.
- Run locally: `npm run dev` (serves `site/`).
- Deploy: GitHub Actions uploads `site/` to Pages on push to `main`.
- Keep root-relative asset paths (`/css/`, `/images/`, `/js/`).
- Research pages: `site/research/<slug>/index.html`.
- Nav scroll-spy lives in `site/js/nav.js`; hero canvas in `site/js/hero.js`.
